Text: There needs to be more breakbeats on these damn sites. Baby Anne is one of the best, I've seen her live a half dozen times down here in Florida and she never has an empty club or a dissapointed crowd. She's gorgeous, and she knows how to make your body flow with her mix!

I totally agree Gemini6678.  This site really needs more breakbeats.  And Baby Anne does fucking rock.  I catch here when I can in Fl too.  I opted to check her instead of Tiesto at Bang fest.  Awesome artist.
